  "text": "With regard to the selective assessment of the MC and PC visual pathways, a recent psychophysical test was designed to measure the contrast sensitivity mediated to MC and PC pathways [CITATION_1] . However, the time to conclude the test is very long, making it difficult to use it for clinical purposes.",
